---
/**
 * context-engineering/0003 · Figure 1 — "Same goal, two doors" (hero).
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from
 * docs/context-engineering/lessons/0003-codebase-context-chunking-and-rag.html
 * (figure + svg + figcaption incl. the footnote <sup>). It lives as an .astro
 * component, NOT inline in the MDX, because MDX's JSX parser is unreliable with
 * raw inline SVG that uses kebab-case attributes (text-anchor, font-size,
 * stroke-width, marker-end, …) and self-referential ids.
 *
 * The source page defines four shared arrowhead <marker>s (#arw, #arwG, #arwR,
 * #arwM) once in a hidden global <svg> in <body>; every figure on the page
 * references them via marker-end="url(#…)". That hidden defs block is reproduced
 * here, in the FIRST figure on the page, so the markers resolve document-wide
 * for Figs 1–5 (ids are kept as-is to match the source DOM and the #s1 anchors).
 */
---

<svg width="0" height="0" style="position:absolute" aria-hidden="true"
    ><defs>
        <marker
            id="arw"
            viewBox="0 0 10 10"
            refX="8.5"
            refY="5"
            markerWidth="7"
            markerHeight="7"
            orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#6b675f"></path></marker
        >
        <marker
            id="arwG"
            viewBox="0 0 10 10"
            refX="8.5"
            refY="5"
            markerWidth="7"
            markerHeight="7"
            orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#2f5d3a"></path></marker
        >
        <marker
            id="arwR"
            viewBox="0 0 10 10"
            refX="8.5"
            refY="5"
            markerWidth="7"
            markerHeight="7"
            orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#9a2417"></path></marker
        >
        <marker
            id="arwM"
            viewBox="0 0 10 10"
            refX="8.5"
            refY="5"
            markerWidth="7"
            markerHeight="7"
            orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#b5179e"></path></marker
        >
    </defs></svg
>

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 640 250"
        role="img"
        aria-label="A giant repo is reduced through indexing or live tools, file and symbol discovery, dependency traversal, and assembly into the window."
    >
        <!-- repo -->
        <rect
            x="22"
            y="96"
            width="120"
            height="58"
            rx="10"
            fill="#efe7f0"
            stroke="#111110"
            stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
        <text x="82" y="120" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#111110"
            >Repository</text
        >
        <text x="82" y="136" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f">~2M tokens</text>
        <!-- two strategies -->
        <rect
            x="186"
            y="36"
            width="150"
            height="46"
            rx="9"
            fill="#f1eef2"
            stroke="#b5179e"
            stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
        <text x="261" y="56" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" font-weight="700" fill="#b5179e"
            >Pre-indexed embeddings</text
        >
        <text x="261" y="71" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
            >Cursor · semantic recall</text
        >
        <rect
            x="186"
            y="168"
            width="150"
            height="46"
            rx="9"
            fill="#e9f3ec"
            stroke="#2f5d3a"
            stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
        <text x="261" y="188" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" font-weight="700" fill="#2f5d3a"
            >Live tools (read-on-demand)</text
        >
        <text x="261" y="203" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
            >Claude Code · grep/read</text
        >
        <!-- discovery pipeline -->
        <rect x="380" y="36" width="150" height="34" rx="8" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#111110"></rect>
        <text x="455" y="57" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-weight="700" fill="#111110"
            >Discover files</text
        >
        <rect x="380" y="80" width="150" height="34" rx="8" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#111110"></rect>
        <text x="455" y="101" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-weight="700" fill="#111110"
            >Discover symbols</text
        >
        <rect x="380" y="124" width="150" height="34" rx="8" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#111110"></rect>
        <text x="455" y="145" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-weight="700" fill="#111110"
            >Traverse dependencies</text
        >
        <rect x="380" y="168" width="150" height="34" rx="8" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#111110"></rect>
        <text x="455" y="189" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-weight="700" fill="#111110"
            >Assemble window</text
        >
        <!-- arrows repo -> strategies -->
        <line x1="142" y1="118" x2="184" y2="66" stroke="#b5179e" marker-end="url(#arwM)"></line>
        <line x1="142" y1="132" x2="184" y2="184" stroke="#2f5d3a" marker-end="url(#arwG)"></line>
        <!-- strategies -> discovery -->
        <line x1="336" y1="59" x2="378" y2="55" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
        <line x1="336" y1="191" x2="378" y2="187" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
        <!-- discovery chain -->
        <line x1="455" y1="70" x2="455" y2="78" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
        <line x1="455" y1="114" x2="455" y2="122" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
        <line x1="455" y1="158" x2="455" y2="166" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
        <!-- window out -->
        <rect
            x="556"
            y="168"
            width="68"
            height="34"
            rx="8"
            fill="#f1eef2"
            stroke="#b5179e"
            stroke-width="2"></rect>
        <text x="590" y="184" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" font-weight="700" fill="#b5179e"
            >window</text
        >
        <text x="590" y="196" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="#6b675f">~200k</text>
        <line x1="530" y1="185" x2="554" y2="185" stroke="#b5179e" marker-end="url(#arwM)"></line>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        Same goal, two doors. Both paths reduce a 2M-token repo to the few right symbols that fit a
        200k window. <b>Cursor pre-indexes; Claude Code reads on demand</b> — but both must discover files,
        discover symbols, and follow dependencies before assembling.<sup
            ><a href="#s2" id="r2">2</a></sup
        >
    </figcaption>
</figure>
